headline.main: Drive Is Opened to Buy Seeds for British; Aim Is to Sell 300,000 Packets at $1 Each

lead_paragraph: A drive for $300,000 with which to purchase and ship to the British seeds for backyard gardens was launched yesterday by the British War Relief Society, 730 Fifth Avenue.
abstract: N Y C Brit War Relief Soc launches fund drive to buy vegetable seeds for planting, illus
